---
// Static CTA section — no dynamic content needed
---

<section data-navbar="dark" class="relative bg-[#1D0084] overflow-hidden py-36">
  <div aria-hidden class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[1000px] h-[700px]"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(11,109,240,0.45) 0%, transparent 65%)"
    />
  </div>
  <div aria-hidden class="absolute inset-0 dots-dark pointer-events-none" />
  <div aria-hidden class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/15 to-transparent" />

  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <div class="sr space-y-8">

      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#025dc7] text-[#e0f2ff] eyebrow">
        <svg class="w-3 h-3 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none">
          <path d="M2 6.5l2.5 2.5 5.5-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        Empieza hoy
      </span>

      <h2 class="display text-white">
        El momento de hablar{' '}
        <span class="text-[#4da3ff]">neerlandés</span>
        <br />es ahora.
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[19px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Únete a los más de 600 hispanohablantes que ya avanzan con método, comunidad y resultados reales.
      </p>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap pt-2">
        <a
          href="/lista-de-espera"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-7 py-3.5 text-[15px] font-semibold rounded-xl bg-[#4da3ff] text-[#0a1a4a] hover:bg-[#3391f0] hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Lista de espera
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contacto"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-7 py-3.5 text-[15px] font-semibold rounded-xl border border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/55 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Contactar con la academia
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-[13px] text-white/30 pt-2">
        Sin compromiso · Orientación inicial gratuita
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
